snippet.title: Shocking! Jack Sparrow படுகாயம் | Jhonny Depp, Amber Heard, Divorce, Pirates of the Caribbean | News
snippet.description:
Pirates of the Caribbean' actor Johnny Depp has submitted pictures of him lying on a stretcher with a severed fingertip to a British court on Tuesday. The actor has alleged that the reason for his condition was his wife Amber Heard.
